summary.description:
Today, cooler for the feels like temperature (down 7.0°C), outside temperature (down 5.9°C), and inside temperature (down 2.8°C) and more moisture-laden outside humidity (up 7%).

Compared to today, yesterday also had noticeable differences in cloud levels (up 517 m).

The past week and month had observable variation in feels like temperature (up 8.5°C), cloud levels (up 494 m), dew point temperature (up 5.9°C), and outside temperature (up 7.1°C) when compared to today.
